N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 9650.1 - Responsibility for repayment of overpayments

State Regulations

Participants are responsible for repaying the value of any
benefits or payments made under the program that were based on applications or
claims submitted in violation of the eligibility requirements of the
program. Notes
